---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <style>
      main { width: 960px; }
      .wrap { width: 760px; max-width: calc(100% - 2em); margin: 3rem auto; padding: 0 1em; line-height: 1.8; }
      h1 { line-height: 1.15; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; }
      .lead { color: rgb(var(--gray-dark)); margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0; }
      .chips { margin: 1rem 0 1.25rem 0; color: rgb(var(--gray)); }
      .chips span { margin-right: .75rem; }
      .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
      .card { border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1rem; }
      .card h2 { margin: 0 0 .5rem 0; font-size: 1.1rem; }
      .card p { margin: 0; color: rgb(var(--gray-dark)); }
      .actions { margin-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      a.btn { display: inline-block; padding: .65rem .9rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; text-decoration: none; }
      a.btn:hover { box-shadow: var(--box-shadow); }
      @media (max-width: 720px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="wrap">
        <h1>Public lab for curiosity-driven experiments.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          新しい技術や未知の領域を試しながら、気づきと仮説を短く残す公開ラボです。
          完成した結論より、思考の途中経過と検証ログを大切にします。
        </p>

        <div class="chips">
          <span>#Cloud (AWS/Azure)</span>
          <span>#AI</span>
          <span>#Architecture</span>
          <span>#Governance</span>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
          <div class="card">
            <h2>Cloud notes</h2>
            <p>Cloud を触って気づいたこと、勘所</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h2>AI experiments</h2>
            <p>生成AI・エージェント・周辺設計を試して共有</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h2>Architecture & governance</h2>
            <p>“動く”より“回る”を重視。統制は加速のための構造</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h2>Work notes</h2>
            <p>企業での意思決定・進め方・学び方など、軽い観察ログ</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn" href="/blog">→ Read the notes</a>
          <a class="btn" href="/about">→ About this lab</a>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 1.75rem; color: rgb(var(--gray));">
          Connect: LinkedIn（必要な場合のみ）
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>